{"name":"xbox-ctrl","version":"1.2.3","description":"Node api for the xbox controller","main":"dist/index.js","bin":{"xbox-ctrl":"bin/xbox-ctrl","xctrl":"bin/xbox-ctrl"},"scripts":{"test":"npm run lint","lint":"eslint lib --fix","precommit":"npm test","commitmsg":"validate-commit-msg","build":"babel lib -d dist","prepublish":"npm run build","install":"prebuild --install"},"repository":"https://github.com/noamokman/xbox-ctrl","keywords":["xbox","native","xinput","windows","controller"],"license":"MIT","homepage":"https://github.com/noamokman/xbox-ctrl#readme","engines":{"node":">=4"},"dependencies":{"bindings":"^1.2.1","commander":"^2.9.0","inquirer":"^1.2.2","nan":"^2.4.0","update-notifier":"^1.0.2","prebuild":"^4.3.0"},"devDependencies":{"babel-cli":"^6.16.0","babel-preset-env":"0.0.6","eslint":"^3.8.1","eslint-config-noamokman":"^5.0.1","husky":"^0.11.9","validate-commit-msg":"^2.8.2"},"gitHead":"a9a2df8024abd732dd339ba9c93f5404710ec178","versions":[{"number":"1.0.0","date":"2016-02-21T18:54:56.202Z"},{"number":"1.0.1","date":"2016-02-22T16:16:08.056Z"},{"number":"1.1.0","date":"2016-09-14T13:19:54.084Z"},{"number":"1.2.0","date":"2016-09-21T18:30:32.352Z"},{"number":"1.2.1","date":"2016-09-21T19:58:24.266Z"},{"number":"1.2.2","date":"2016-10-24T12:12:01.542Z"},{"number":"1.2.3","date":"2016-10-24T12:47:51.069Z"}],"readme":"# xbox-ctrl\nNode api for the xbox controller\n\n## Installation\nAs cli tool\n``` bash\n$ [sudo] npm install xbox-ctrl -g\n```\n\nProgrammatically\n``` bash\n$ [sudo] npm install xbox-ctrl --save\n```\n\n## Usage\n### CLI\n#### Options\n``` bash\n$ xbox-ctrl --help\n\n  Usage: xbox-ctrl <command>\n\n\n  Commands:\n\n    off [options] [controllers...]      Turn off controllers\n    vibrate [options] [controllers...]  Vibrate controllers\n    list                                List connected controllers\n\n  Node api for the xbox controller\n\n  Options:\n\n    -h, --help     output usage information\n    -V, --version  output the version number\n\n\n```\n#### Synonym\nThis module is exported as `xbox-ctrl` and as `xctrl`.\n\n### Programmatically\n#### Example\n``` js\nconst xboxCtrl = require('xbox-ctrl');\n\n// list connected controllers\nxboxCtrl.list(); // => [1, 2]\n\n// turns off controller 1\nxboxCtrl.off(1);\n\n// turns off all controllers\nxboxCtrl.offAll();\n\n// vibrate controller 1\nxboxCtrl.vibrate(1);\n\n// vibrate all controllers\nxboxCtrl.vibrateAll();\n```\n\n## License\n\n[MIT](LICENSE)\n","created":"2016-02-21T18:54:56.202Z","modified":"2016-10-24T12:47:51.069Z","lastPublisher":{"name":"noamokman","email":"noamokman@gmail.com"},"owners":[{"name":"noamokman","email":"noamokman@gmail.com"}],"other":{"_attachments":{},"_from":".","_id":"xbox-ctrl","_nodeVersion":"6.8.0","_npmOperationalInternal":{"host":"packages-18-east.internal.npmjs.com","tmp":"tmp/xbox-ctrl-1.2.3.tgz_1477313269566_0.014794995076954365"},"_npmUser":{"name":"noamokman","email":"noamokman@gmail.com"},"_npmVersion":"3.10.8","_rev":"3-127b711d49c8e15ad1d2df89c2acc844","_shasum":"0c232b1ea1bdd4dee3f6639229144cc237a1b3ca","author":{"name":"Noam Okman","email":"noamokman@gmail.com","url":"https://github.com/noamokman"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/noamokman/xbox-ctrl/issues"},"directories":{},"dist-tags":{"latest":"1.2.3"},"dist":{"shasum":"0c232b1ea1bdd4dee3f6639229144cc237a1b3ca","tarball":"http://registry.npmjs.org/xbox-ctrl/-/xbox-ctrl-1.2.3.tgz"},"maintainers":[{"name":"noamokman","email":"noamokman@gmail.com"}],"readmeFilename":"README.md","time":{"modified":"2016-10-24T12:47:51.069Z","created":"2016-02-21T18:54:56.202Z","1.0.0":"2016-02-21T18:54:56.202Z","1.0.1":"2016-02-22T16:16:08.056Z","1.1.0":"2016-09-14T13:19:54.084Z","1.2.0":"2016-09-21T18:30:32.352Z","1.2.1":"2016-09-21T19:58:24.266Z","1.2.2":"2016-10-24T12:12:01.542Z","1.2.3":"2016-10-24T12:47:51.069Z"}}}